Five stars resort built in Moroccan style, located directly on the Red Sea shores of Makadi  Bay in 
Hurghada, at  36km to the south from Hurghada International Airport.

elevated garden overlooking the sea; while the Spa, the gym, the tenni s court, the safari quad-bikes

Serenity Alpha Beach offers mul tiple gastronomic choices throughout numer ous restaurants &
